verbose_text: Serum amylase levels (mean +/- SD) before FCSEMS placement, 3 hours after the procedure, the next day, and two days later were 99.9 +/- 159.6, 153.7 +/- 155.9, 231.5 +/- 285.9, and 179.6 +/- 143.9 for the EST group and 77.4 +/- 71.3, 125.6 +/- 101.6, 185.1 +/- 192.3, and 145.3 +/- 204.1 for the non EST group, showing no significant differences (NS; XREF_FIG).
